---
// Features.astro - Componente de recursos/funcionalidades
---

<section id="features" class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-fade-in-up">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        Funcionalidades Completas para <span class="gradient-text">Alunos, Instrutores e Administração</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        O melhor software de autoescola com todos os recursos: agendamento online, gestão de aulas, controle de veículos, relatórios financeiros e muito mais.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Tabs for User Types -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center mb-12 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
      <button class="tab-button active px-8 py-3 bg-[#6f0a59] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-2" data-tab="alunos">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">school</span>
        Alunos
      </button>
      <button class="tab-button px-8 py-3 border-2 border-[#6f0a59] text-[#6f0a59] dark:border-white dark:text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#6f0a59] hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-white dark:hover:text-[#6f0a59] transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-2" data-tab="instrutores">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">person_raised_hand</span>
        Instrutores
      </button>
      <button class="tab-button px-8 py-3 border-2 border-[#6f0a59] text-[#6f0a59] dark:border-white dark:text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#6f0a59] hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-white dark:hover:text-[#6f0a59] transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-2" data-tab="admin">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">admin_panel_settings</span>
        Administração
      </button>
    </div>

    <!-- Tab Content: Alunos -->
    <div id="tab-alunos" class="tab-content grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16 animate-fade-in">
      <div class="feature-card bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-[#6f0a59] transition-all duration-300">
