        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Agendamento 24/7</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Marque aulas qualquer hora, em qualquer lugar pelo celular</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-[#6f0a59] transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4 text-[#6f0a59]"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl">calendar_month</span></div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Calendário Visual</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">Veja horários disponíveis em tempo real antes de marcar</p>
      </div>

